## Run auth.http → Login first to populate {{token}}

###
## ─── Gathering Skills ───
###

### Get gathering skill levels
GET {{host}}/gathering/skills
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
## ─── Gathering Nodes ───
###

### Get nearby gathering nodes (must be at a node's coordinates)
GET {{host}}/gathering/nodes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
## ─── Harvest ───
###

### Harvest from a copper vein (must be at 37,26)
POST {{host}}/gathering/harvest
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "nodeId": "copper-vein-1"
}

### Harvest from a wildflower patch (must be at 50,10)
POST {{host}}/gathering/harvest
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "nodeId": "wildflower-patch-1"
}

### Harvest from a pine stand (must be at 50,11)
POST {{host}}/gathering/harvest
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "nodeId": "pine-stand-1"
}
